{"tid":1029257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【象牙女王】中國大媽走私2噸象牙 遭坦桑尼亞判監15年","createTime":"2019-02-20T06:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T07:09:19.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7d242f03b60039038b50fe9a8466107201db58","tid":1029257,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190220/large/1550629417_e1af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190220%2Flarge%2F1550629417_e1af.jpg&h=33408dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「象牙女王」楊鳳蘭遭判監15年。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n綽號「象牙女王」的中國女商人楊鳳蘭，被非洲坦桑尼亞法院判處監禁15年，罪名是組織往來於亞洲和坦桑尼亞的犯罪集團。<br />\n<br />\n楊鳳蘭與兩名坦桑尼亞男子於當地時間19日一起被起訴，他們在2000至2004年期間走私860件、重達2噸的象牙，受害大象多達400頭。此外，被起訴的兩名男子也分別被判監15年。<br />\n<br />\n這3名被告還同時被判罰款1,300萬美元（約1億港元），否則將會加刑。這一數額是他們所走私象牙製品市場價值的兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n坦桑尼亞警方稱，69歲的楊鳳蘭自1970年代起於坦桑尼亞居住，曾擔任坦桑尼亞中非商會副會長，也當地一間知名中餐館的老闆。坦桑尼亞國家和跨國重罪調查組經一年多追查，於2015年10月將她拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"9dd385aff9d57dc466ed4c48bbeffb36b01dc200","tid":1029257,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"老野唔讓位咪整9你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41117a40ac00abc824ecdf24e126b28c1e4ecadd","tid":1029257,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"15年咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c38b87cef471dc892fc84fca0a25321dc40fa5","tid":1029257,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"69<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430cde1a83e2fbed4d47155999209674447e901b","tid":1029257,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"69歲的楊鳳蘭自1970年代起於坦桑尼亞居住，曾擔任坦桑尼亞中非商會副會長，也當地一間知名中餐館的老闆。<br />\n<br />\n好似Breaking Bad 個炸雞店店長"},{"pid":"b7bf49acb2f618ca1d4b77075815061dfb6ec287","tid":1029257,"uid":129169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41117a40ac00abc824ecdf24e126b28c1e4ecadd","tid":1029257,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"15年咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:09:19.000Z","msg":"冇錢比加倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}